{
  "stem": "18960.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I grabbed him by the neck and I threw him down the scaffold.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "To threw down the-- throw down the kapo off my scaffold was a certain death.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a-- he was an untouchable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I-- in desperation, I did it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And to make sure, I pushed the-- some bricks in the mortar, also from the thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everything fell down-- made it appear like it was an accident.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he-- he himself knew it was no accident that I pushed him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I came down the scaffold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "All my friends, the Poles, came running to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "What's happened here?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I said, you know what he said?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He suspected me I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then they started beating up on him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were so upset that he dared to suspect me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So from that moment on-- point on, that kapo never reported the incident.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He never did, lucky for me. but He avoided me like a plague.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Whenever he saw me, he just went the other way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So that think was the most critical moment of my being in Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I would have acted differently, I would probably-- it would have been the end of me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I would have turned pale or something-- so that was that incident.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let me just bring up another incident-- another incident, but it was a routine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every Saturday night, the whole block, the whole barrack, had to proceed to so-called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody had to strip naked, and the [GERMAN], so-called-- the charge of the, of the wing, of that, of that barrack-- checked for lice-- checked-- checked at the-- by the genitals, under the armpits, because there was-- there was a lot of lice.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every Saturday night was a nightmare for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I figured, this is the end of me.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
